songs.title: Interlude 1
songs.lyrics:
[Interlude]
Good evening fellow earth people
Tonight I would like to take you on a trip
A trip with our minds
We're going to do something a little unique this evening
Start by just relaxing in your chairs and feel your consciousness
Feel where you are
I think most will find your self awareness
Somewhere up here in the cranium
That's where I dwell, that's where your center of awareness is
Self awareness, mind
Self awareness, mind

[Instrumental]

Cranium
We're going to do something a little unique this evening

[Instrumental]

Self awareness, mind
Cranium

[Instrumental]

[Outro]
That's where I dwell
That's where your center of awareness is
Mind
